<seg id="7">On the basis of a statement made by the tenant in the Subletting Agreement, the tenant's husband (Mr Martin Bureš, No: 760305/3920) expressed his agreement to the conclusion of the Subletting Agreement before signing the Subletting Agreement.</seg>
