<seg id="83">Conduct of the inspection operation in the SRN</seg>
<seg id="84">The audit was carried out between June 2006 and February 2007 by the Indirect Taxation Audit Group and the personnel of the designated regional audit offices in Berlin, Frankfurt am Main and Munich.</seg>
<seg id="85">The inspection was part of the 2006 control plan and was therefore notified to the Federal Ministry in 2006.</seg>
<seg id="86">After the testing phase, the review started in the fourth quarter of 2006.</seg>
<seg id="87">According to cases selected by BRH and later selected SAIs, BRH had to notify a number of federal states of control.</seg>
<seg id="88">In addition to the talks at the Federal MF and the CLO, the audit was carried out in the following federal states:</seg>
